OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThe lesbian activist       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fseeking marriage equality  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fin India                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, With India's Supreme Court due to rule 
OL,6, on legalising same-sex marriages in the
OL,7, coming days, Maya Sharma is waiting    
OL,8, with trepidation for the verdict.      
OL,10,FAn LGBTQ+ activist, the 73-year-old    
OL,11,Flives with her female partner in the   
OL,12,Fwestern city of Vadodara.              
OL,14,FShe is among the 21 petitioners,       
OL,15,Fincluding same-sex couples, trans      
OL,16,Fpeople and organisations, who are      
OL,17,Fseeking marriage equality. Her plea,   
OL,18,Ffiled along with nine others, also     
OL,19,Fwants the right for LGBTQ+ people to   
OL,20,Fchoose their families, even outside of 
OL,21,Fmarriage.                              
